<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_27" id="13r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab facs="#facs_27_r1l2"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Conrad<ex>en</ex></expan> Bẏſſchoff cʒu Olmuͦncʒ vnd
                                <expan>Oberſt<ex>en</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_27_r1l3"><expan>Camr<ex>er</ex></expan> des künigreichs cʒu
                        Beheim <expan cert="medium">d<ex>etur</ex></expan></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_27_r1l4">Gnedıger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> Als wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> hochwirdıkeit voꝛmals <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_27_r1l5">von Conrad Glancʒ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> burgers vnd der ſchulde wegen als Jm </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_27_r1l6">Arnolt Puſch von Cöln ſelig ſchuldig <expan>blıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> iſt / Alſo kümt derſelb ~ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_27_r1l7"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> <expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan> aber cʒu <expan>ew<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>fürſtenlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gnaden von <expan>derſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ~ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_27_r1l8"><expan>ſein<ex>er</ex></expan> ſchulde wegen / <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> daʒ Jm <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> darẏnne <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> günſtige </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_27_r1l9">hılff vnd <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> gnedıklich beweiſen wölle / Als etc / Das <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_27_r1l11"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> fe </del> <expan>Sabb<ex>a</ex>to</expan> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Michaelis Anno ix<hi rend="sup">no</hi></ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter"><ab facs="#facs_27_r1l13">Dem edeln veſten <expan>Laurencʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ʒeẏſelmeiſt<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_27_r1l14">des künigreichs cʒu Beheim hofrichter / ſı<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_27" id="13r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Conrad<ex>en</ex></expan>, Bysschoff czu Olmuͦncz und
                                <expan>oberst<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>camr<ex>er</ex></expan> des künigreichs czu Beheim <note place="inline"><expan cert="medium">d<ex>etur</ex></expan></note>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Gnediger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> hochwirdikeit vormals
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von Conrad Glancz,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> burgers, und der schulde wegen, als im
                        Arnolt Pusch von Cöln, selig, schuldig <expan>blib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ist.
                        Also kümt derselb <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>
<expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan> aber czu <expan>ew<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gnaden von
                            <expan>derselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>sein<ex>er</ex></expan> schulde wegen.
                            <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz im <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> darynne <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
                        günstige hilff und <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> gnediklich beweisen
                        wölle, als etc. Das <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sabb<ex>a</ex>to</expan>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Michaelis anno ix<hi rend="sup">no</hi>.</ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter">
<ab>Dem edeln, vesten <expan>Laurencze<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Zeyselmeist<ex>er</ex></expan>, des künigreichs czu Beheim hofrichter
                            si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
